            <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrc="filepath:1;25:23" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/topicref.dita">setup.dita</filepath> uses the <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:1;25:62" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/topicref.dita">collection-type</xmlatt> attribute to
          indicate that the order of three sub-topics in that section is important.</p><codeblock class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xml:space="preserve" xtrc="codeblock:1;26:99" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/topicref.dita">&lt;map&gt;
